text: Dilo is standard Spanish for "say it". It may also refer to: ==People== * Christopher Dilo (born 1994), French footballer * Dilo Doxan (born 1984), Kurdish Syrian musician ==Places== * Dilo, Bourgogne-Franche-Comté, France, former commune now part of Arces-Dilo * Dilo River, Gabon ==Other== * Dilo oil tree, also known as Calophyllum inophyllum ==See also== * Day in the life of (disambiguation)
title: Dilo
